PROGRAM PHOTOS
==============

Each program needs TWO images: a card thumbnail and a hero banner.
Place them in the matching subfolder (master-dddi/, fab-academy/, etc.).

---- CARD THUMBNAIL ----
Filename:  card.jpg
Size:      800 × 500 px  (16:10 ratio)
Used on:   Program cards on the homepage and /programs/ page

---- HERO BANNER ----
Filename:  hero.jpg
Size:      1600 × 700 px  (wide landscape)
Used on:   Top of each individual program page

STYLE NOTES
-----------
- Show learning in action: workshops, presentations, students collaborating.
- Hero banners work best as wide horizontal shots — avoid portrait orientation.
- The hero will have text overlaid, so leave some visual breathing room.

